## Command Router Implementation

### Approach
Build a **local command router** (`CommandRouter`) that pattern-matches user input to predefined intents. Each intent maps to one or more tool calls. Gemini API is used as fallback only for unrecognized queries.

### All Predefined Commands

```
NAVIGATION:
  "open/show dashboard"        → navigate('/dashboard')
  "open/show plants"           → navigate('/plants')
  "open/show inverters"        → navigate('/inverters')
  "open/show slms"             → navigate('/slmsDevices')
  "open/show sensors"          → navigate('/sensors')
  "go back"                    → window.history.back()

PLANTS:
  "open {name} plant"          → navigate('/plants') → click plant card
  "search plant {query}"       → navigate('/plants') → type in search

PLANT DETAIL (chained):
  "{name} energy"              → open plant → click Energy tab
  "{name} revenue"             → open plant → click Revenue tab
  "{name} monthly energy"      → open plant → Energy → Monthly
  "{name} yearly revenue"      → open plant → Revenue → Yearly
  "{name} lifetime energy"     → open plant → Energy → LifeTime

DASHBOARD TABS:
  "show energy"                → click Energy tab
  "show revenue"               → click Revenue tab
  "show monthly"               → click Monthly
  "show yearly"                → click Yearly
  "show lifetime"              → click LifeTime

SENSORS:
  "open sensor {name}"         → navigate('/sensors') → click sensor row
  "filter {type} sensors"      → navigate('/sensors') → click tab
  "show wms sensors"           → navigate('/sensors') → WMS tab
  "show temperature sensors"   → navigate('/sensors') → Temperature tab
  "show mfm sensors"           → navigate('/sensors') → MFM tab

SENSOR DETAIL:
  "sensor value"               → read h5 value
  "sensor name"                → read h2 name
  "sensor category"            → read h6 category
  "set date {DD/MM/YYYY}"      → set datepicker value

INVERTERS:
  "search inverter {query}"    → navigate('/inverters') → type in search
  "open inverter {name}"       → navigate('/inverters') → click row

GENERIC:
  "click {text}"               → click element by text
  "read page"                  → read page content
  "scroll down/up"             → scroll page
  "show alerts"                → click Alerts button
```

### Files to Change

#### [NEW] [command_router.dart](file:///d:/HACKAMIND/aalok_dashboard/lib/services/command_router.dart)
- Keyword/pattern matching engine
- Each command has: keywords, parameter extraction regex, and an execute function
- Returns `CommandResult` with response text and executed actions

#### [MODIFY] [home_screen.dart](file:///d:/HACKAMIND/aalok_dashboard/lib/screens/home_screen.dart)
- Try `CommandRouter.match()` first → if matched, execute locally
- If no match → fall back to Gemini [LlmService](file:///d:/HACKAMIND/aalok_dashboard/lib/services/llm_service.dart#8-249)

#### [MODIFY] [tool_registry.dart](file:///d:/HACKAMIND/aalok_dashboard/lib/tools/tool_registry.dart)
- Add combined/chained tool methods (e.g. `openPlantByName`, `showPlantRevenue`)

#### [MODIFY] [navigation_tools.dart](file:///d:/HACKAMIND/aalok_dashboard/lib/tools/navigation_tools.dart)
- Fix SLMs route to `/slmsDevices` (currently `/slms`)

